{"word":"αὔτως","slug":"αὔτως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n18047\" key=\"au)/tws\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">αὔτως</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>: <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n18047.0\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in this very manner, even so,</tr_> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">γυμνὸν ἐόντα αὔ. ὥς τε γυναῖκα</foreign> unarmed <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">just as I am</tr_> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">like</abbr> a woman, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:125\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.125</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in the self-same way, likewise,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σὺν δ᾽ αὔ. ἐγώ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg002.perseus-grc1:85\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ant.\">Ant.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">85</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Numen.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0008.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:328d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.328d</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὔ. ὅπωσπερ</foreign>. . <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1179\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Aj.\">