orm=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">235.5</biblScope></bibl>, al.); but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὕτως</foreign> is usu. written in codd. of Trag. Gramm. were divided as to etym. and accent, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0082.tlg002:174:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.D.\">A.D.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">174.1</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4099.tlg001:172:34\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ EM\">EM</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">172.34</biblScope></bibl>, and distd. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὕτως</foreign> 'likewise' from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὔτως</foreign> 'in vain'. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4066.tlg003:178\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dam.\">Dam.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pr.\">Pr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">178</biblScope> </bibl> uses <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὕτως,</foreign> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">of itself</tr_> (from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αὑτοῦ</foreign>).)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}